name: Natalia
description: I am seeking a good man for intelligent conversation, a best friend for good and bad time as well. I have had many heart breaks in my life. I do not complain. It is natural and makes us stronger in the end. I was really hurt in my past and I promised myself never to love anymore but later become fully aware that I need to forget about the past and face the future. I remain an eternal optimist, since I do seek a good man still. I am very simple lady and I love everyone as the way I treat myself, whether white or black, rich or poor and I don’t care where you from because we are all with the same color of blood.
